snippet.title: Gray Zone Warfare Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Gray Zone Warfare is an immersive tactical first-person shooter with a maximum focus on realism. Become a part of a Private Military Company and navigate an expansive open-world setting alone or in a squad. Adapt to your surroundings, use tactics to your advantage, and fight for survival against other human operators and AI-controlled enemies.

Wishlist now at
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2479810

Learn more at
https://www.grayzonewarfare.com/

Enter the Gray Zone on Discord
https://discord.gg/grayzonewarfare

Follow 
http://twitter.com/grayzonewarfare

#tacticalshooter #fps #steamgame #unrealengine
